        "height": 660,
        "content": "## 2. Use Custom Workflow Tool for More Complex Commands\n[Learn more about the Execute Command tool](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/core-nodes/n8n-nodes-base.executecommand/)\n\n"
